{
  "id": "RAW_e26138f0",
  "title": "OpenAI 紧急发布 GPT-5.1-Codex-Max，带来「长程任务能力」，可 24 小时工作",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&mid=2247499652&idx=1&sn=11d1e3eeb0ea187e1fc299bea8345f7a",
  "date": "2025-11-20 04:50:00",
  "author": "刘小排",
  "siteName": "刘小排r",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=717d1e80&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F607DKnuWzlFtTvdYEtWZ39y1yPqFcan9icicvzsMJQFJlwtgrQMGfG9fMwlRNKdJyhlDCXBqTXfkZjcsxIoWUKyA%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">哈喽，大家好，我是刘小排。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">真是太激动了啊，哈哈哈，让不让人睡觉了还。过去两天，先是Gemini 3 Pro、然后是GPT-5.1-Codex-Max和GPT-5.1 Pro，一个比一个好。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">有粉丝催更，我快速总结几句吧。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"background-color:rgb(255, 104, 39);\">省流版</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">1.&nbsp;<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">综合</span>编程能力 &nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 41, 65);\">GPT-5.1-Codex-Max</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">&nbsp; &gt; Gemini 3 Pro &gt;&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">GPT-5.1-Codex &nbsp;&gt;&gt; Claude Sonnet 4.5&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">2. 但是，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Gemini 3 Pro 的前端能力极强</span>，<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">我并不认为&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">GPT-5.1-Codex-Max的前端表现能超过</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Gemini 3 Pro</span>。 因此，在今天，我的选择是</span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li style=\"color:#ff6827;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">前端任务： 用</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">Gemini 3 Pro</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"color:#ff6827;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">其他一切： 用GPT-5.1-Codex-Max&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li style=\"color:#ff6827;\">\n    <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">不再需要： Claude Sonnet 4.5&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">3.&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">GPT-5.1-Codex-Max&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">除了编程</span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">能力重新登顶，</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">还带来的新特性：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);font-weight: bold;\">长程任务能力</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">。原生训练支持多上下文窗口、24小时工作。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">朋友们，如果你们想用Codex来复刻</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzI1MTUxNzgxMA==&amp;mid=2247498770&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=0b252c03df0fbac24d6aec1dc15bf6cc&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致 | 对话刘小排\" data-itemshowtype=\"8\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">揭秘 Claude Code 榜一大哥：一个 AI 创业者如何把工具用到极致 | 对话刘小排</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;现在变得很容易了</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">提供更长时思考的Extra High（xhigh）模式，大力出奇迹</span>。注意：日常推荐medium，只有特别难的任务才需要用high和xhigh</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </ul>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"2 2 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">4.&nbsp;</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:null},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:&quot;mp-quote&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;line-height:1.6;font-style:normal;\">GPT-5.1-Codex-Max 可以通过<span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Codex CLI、Codex IDE Extension使用</span>，暂时无法通过API使用。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016000\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.33240740740740743\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b44cc992&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFtTvdYEtWZ39y1yPqFcan9oOzIHLmpfOFIAzn9Gpkurm2AFZ307WggOe7o9WGybA84jsicLvUyS0A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100016001\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.35294117647058826\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1054\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0c55e8fe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFtTvdYEtWZ39y1yPqFcan92ic73PsVj9sdWrmmfguwA1snFIXH7GAswrldXpqCqT4F19sLzTgKnVQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这次发布，OpenAI一改以前高调的作风，让人很不习惯。没有视频、没有发布后，只有两条孤零零的Twitter。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015989\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5342592592592592\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=cdd85bca&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFtTvdYEtWZ39y1yPqFcan9uVQ5I5oSvMs7RSfUNTnhVYv6UsXFsnyZgb8Vms2DMMKcHuZTq5Lnsg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015990\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0138888888888888\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=592bc0c0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFtTvdYEtWZ39y1yPqFcan9TgPiacLjkZzXWVD0QkAZ5Yz4nVf9qHdSNDgIzc6rUanWIJicnawplOdg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">在OpenAI的技术博文，它重点强调了GPT-5.1-Codex-Max 能够连续工作24小时的能力。</span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015993\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.24722222222222223\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=492c203e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFtTvdYEtWZ39y1yPqFcan9XVxghUhkDeS0PSicIMTZCpbVO11McSUYhE1HmnR3546sj5kiaBdFiaKOw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是因为，</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">GPT-5.1-Codex-Max 是OpenAI首个「原生训练支持多窗口上下文」机制的模型，可以跨越多个上下文工作。</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">所谓</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 104, 39);\">「原生训练支持多窗口上下文」机制</span></span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">，并不是OpenAI首创。Claude 系列模型已经在几个月前开始了，9月Claude Sonnet 4.5刚刚发布时，它也是可以连续工作超过24小时的。</span></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\">Peter Gostev大神用GPT-5.1-Codex-Max(Extra-High)的长程任务能力，做了高级金门大桥场景，感叹道：&nbsp;</span></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">效果是他见过最好的</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p><span leaf=\"\">Gemini 3 Pro也能做，但是没</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">GPT-5.1-Codex-Max(Extra-High)好。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">下面两个截图，图1是</span><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">GPT-5.1-Codex-Max(Extra-High) ，图2是 Gemini 3 Pro做的。</span></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015994\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7462962962962963\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e942780e&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFtTvdYEtWZ39y1yPqFcan9AzicI9l3v2Zdn6QACEeOFWewt1OwfW6GwZOXUT63ZZc2STgibUddhIAQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100015995\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.8657407407407407\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0d75bdfe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F607DKnuWzlFtTvdYEtWZ39y1yPqFcan9fvgicI716WGEOzaSZVVoN2kHPnibIM3cZoTCIv4nmUibrfmLMzYnhmFwA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">GPT-5.1-Codex-Max(Extra-High) 做得实在是太好了，我把原始视频放出来吧。</span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  </div>\n  <hr style=\"border-style: solid;border-width: 1px 0 0;border-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);-webkit-transform-origin: 0 0;-webkit-transform: scale(1, 0.5);transform-origin: 0 0;transform: scale(1, 0.5);\">\n  <div style=\"text-align: left;\">\n   <p><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;p&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">我写代码去了！期待你的反馈！</span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章快速总结了 OpenAI 最新发布的 GPT-5.1-Codex-Max 模型在编程能力上的突破，特别是其长程任务能力，并将其与 Gemini 3 Pro 等模型进行了对比，提供了实用选择建议。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章快速总结了 OpenAI 最新发布的 GPT-5.1-Codex-Max 模型在编程能力上的突破，特别是其长程任务能力，并将其与 Gemini 3 Pro 等模型进行了对比，提供了实用选择建议。",
  "summary": "文章介绍了 OpenAI 紧急发布的 GPT-5.1-Codex-Max 模型，强调其在综合编程能力上重新登顶，并具备原生训练支持多上下文窗口、可 24 小时工作的长程任务能力，以及提供更长时思考的 Extra High 模式。作者将其与 Gemini 3 Pro 和 Claude Sonnet 4.5 进行对比，明确表示 Gemini 3 Pro 适用于前端任务，GPT-5.1-Codex-Max 适用于其他编程任务，并认为不再需要 Claude Sonnet 4.5。文章指出 OpenAI 此次发布风格低调，并引用外部专家观点验证了 Codex-Max 的长程任务效果，最后提及模型可通过 Codex CLI 和 Codex IDE Extension 使用，暂时无法通过 API 访问。",
